Description: Include cstdint for uint8_t in cppgc/heap-statistics.h
 Newer libstdc++/compiler combinations no longer expose uint8_t
 transitively through the existing includes. Include cstdint directly.
Author: Dockershelf Maintainers <41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
Forwarded: no

--- a/deps/v8/include/cppgc/heap-statistics.h
+++ b/deps/v8/include/cppgc/heap-statistics.h
@@ -8,6 +8,7 @@
 #define INCLUDE_CPPGC_HEAP_STATISTICS_H_
 
